channel.title: Nindota - The August Collection
channel.description:
I listened back on about 220 of my tracks yesterday, and decided to upload 41 of them to YouTube. The first 5 tracks were made in Garageband, but the rest were made entirely in Auxy, with the oldest track dating all the way back to early December 2019.
[The August Collection](https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLhN4j0GKlCc4LICWniltleiVH5m5SFCmv)
